# Financial Risk Operational Expected Loss Offsets Amount

## identifier
de8180

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of any expected loss offset amounts. This item is to be determined in accordance with relevant prudential standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=FinancialRisk.Operational.ExpectedLossOffsets.Amount
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.06
- period=instant
